---
title: Quick Vietnamese-Style Pork & Peanuts with Garlic Rice, Sesame Veggies & Fried Egg
description: Whisk away your tastebuds to the beautiful land of Vietnam with this rice bowl recipe! Juicy pork mince gets a hit of ginger and
hoisin sauce, before being piled on top of aromatic garlic rice and sautéed veggies for an unbeatably simple but elegant meal that’s
wonderfully addictive, light and tasty.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vietnamese-style-pork-peanuts-5178c96a.jpg
